OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1781024765
OL,3,CWorld Cup travel in US could cause
OL,4,Cmore jet fuel shortages in UK, says
OL,5,Cexpert
OL,7,FTravel needs for the World Cup could
OL,8,Flead to jet fuel shortages in the UK
OL,9,Fas an increased numbers of drivers in
OL,10,Fthe United States cause demand for
OL,11,Fgasoline to rise, experts have warned.
OL,13,FThe US is already approaching "driving
OL,14,Fseason" ` a period of increased car
OL,15,Fuse ` which will be intensified by the
OL,16,Ftournament, Eleanor Budds, director of
OL,17,Fresearch in oil markets at S&P Global
OL,18,FEnergy, said during the World Air
OL,19,FTransport Summit in Brazil this week.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
