OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1781024765
OL,3,CWorld Cup travel in US could cause
OL,4,Cmore jet fuel shortages in UK, says
OL,5,Cexpert
OL,7,FGasoline stocks, which are usually
OL,8,Fbuilt up in preparation for the
OL,9,Fperiod, have fallen below the five-
OL,10,Fyear average due to the reduced
OL,11,Fcapacity of the Strait of Hormuz.
OL,13,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
