FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1781024765
OL,3,CWorld Cup travel in US could cause
OL,4,Cmore jet fuel shortages in UK, says
OL,5,Cexpert
OL,7,F"This means that refiners will have to
OL,8,Fpivot some of the extra jet fuel
OL,9,Feffort they've been making, they will
OL,10,Fhave to at some point pivot back to
OL,11,Fgasoline," Budds said during a panel
OL,12,Fin Rio de Janeiro.
OL,14,FThe Strait of Hormuz, through which a
OL,15,Ffifth of the world's oil usually
OL,16,Fpasses, has been almost entirely
OL,17,Fclosed by the conflict in the Middle
OL,18,FEast, which began after joint US-
OL,19,FIsraeli attacks on Iran on February 28.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1781024765
OL,3,CWorld Cup travel in US could cause
OL,4,Cmore jet fuel shortages in UK, says
OL,5,Cexpert
OL,7,FThis has caused the UK to become a
OL,8,Fmajor importer of US fuel, which has
OL,9,Fso far protected the nation from
OL,10,Fshortages for the time being.
OL,12,FBudds also stated that she expects
OL,13,Ffuel prices to get worse before they
OL,14,Fget better, despite the price of Brent
OL,15,FCrude oil appearing to stabilise in
OL,16,Frecent weeks.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1781024765
OL,3,CWorld Cup travel in US could cause
OL,4,Cmore jet fuel shortages in UK, says
OL,5,Cexpert
OL,7,F"We think prices could rise again. The
OL,8,Freason for that is the markets made
OL,9,Fsome small adjustments, but (as seen
OL,10,Fin) the stock levels and the exports,
OL,11,FUS refiners who have plugging a lot of
OL,12,Fthe gap can't necessarily keep doing
OL,13,Fso for jet fuel," Budds said.
OL,15,F"Which suggests to us that gasoline
OL,16,Fprices will rise again, crude prices
OL,17,Fwill rise again and jet fuel prices
OL,18,Fwill rise again, before there's some
OL,19,Fmore stability after the summer
OL,20,Fseason, when demand falls back down
OL,21,Fagain from the peak.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1781024765
OL,3,CWorld Cup travel in US could cause
OL,4,Cmore jet fuel shortages in UK, says
OL,5,Cexpert
OL,7,F"That will allow stocks to start to
OL,8,Frebuild and some normalisation of the
OL,9,Fsituation."
OL,11,FA spokesperson for the Department for
OL,12,FEnergy Security and Net Zero said they
OL,13,Fdid not agree with Budds' assessment
OL,14,Fand that there was no indication that
OL,15,Fjet fuel supply would further be
OL,16,Fimpacted in the UK.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1781024765
OL,3,CWorld Cup travel in US could cause
OL,4,Cmore jet fuel shortages in UK, says
OL,5,Cexpert
OL,7,F"We do not agree with these claims,
OL,8,Fwhich appear to have no analysis
OL,9,Fbehind them," they said. "UK airlines
OL,10,Fare clear that they are not currently
OL,11,Fseeing a shortage of jet fuel and
OL,12,Fholidays are taking off as planned."
OL,14,F"We continue to work with fuel
OL,15,Fsuppliers, airports, airlines and
OL,16,Finternational counterparts to keep
OL,17,Fflights operating."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
