OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1781024765
OL,3,CWorld Cup travel in US could cause
OL,4,Cmore jet fuel shortages in UK, says
OL,5,Cexpert
OL,7,FMillions of football fans are expected
OL,8,Fto watch World Cup games across the
OL,9,FUS, Mexico and Canada this summer,
OL,10,Fwhich kicks off on June 11.
OL,12,FThe tournament has faced controversy
OL,13,Ffor high ticket prices, restrictions
OL,14,Fon fans bringing water bottles and the
OL,15,FTrump administration's immigration
OL,16,Fpolicies, which have seen a referee
OL,17,Fdenied entry to the country.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/8
